  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1561990/extras/8e066e8584d3c166073bb1feeede7981.avif?t=1682376198\" width=648 height=246 /></span><br><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1561990/extras/f9c9b3629b093b014bfb84b29ee2117b.avif?t=1682376198\" width=367 height=79 /></span>.<br><br><br><br>Welcome to the Dark land, better known as Gourland and accompanies <br>this hero through this dangerous land, filled with wild creatures <br>and giant colossus, which will not let you complete your mission.<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1561990/extras/e2130219d50d4ecba040f34cd63322ec.avif?t=1682376198\" width=367 height=79 /></span>.<br><br><br>- 9 levels and 15 maps of the platform action retro 16-bit style.<br><br>- Different routes to explore these dark dungeons.<br><br>- 5 giant boss.<br><br>- Set entirely in pixelart.<br><br>- Increase your weapons and upload level.<br><br>- Soundtrack symphonic rock. <br><br>- Based on the book Tales of the Dark Lands.<br><br>- Difficulty Retro.",
